nodes.text: Around 0 ABY, a bounty hunter was working for the Galactic Empire on Kwenn Space Station, having been contracted to capture Commander Adar Tallon from hiding on Tatooine. Alongside another hunter, she was present when an Alliance to Restore the Republic squad found the body of one of their agents, Dana, at the feet of Imperial lieutenant Voor. She was killed during the ensuing skirmish.
The hunter was short and wiry, and armed with a blaster pistol, blaster rifle, grenade and medpac.
